		<td><b>techniques you've found on your own</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />detuning - doubling instruments at a slightly different pitch
<br />
<br />frequency sweep detuning - doubling an instrument, one with pitch sweeping the other without
<br />
<br />fake reverberation - doubling an instrument only with a little delay to it

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
