<br />
<br /><a href="http://nsf.4x86.com/nsfs/The_Battle_Continues.nsf" class="postlink">2:33 to 2:40</a> playing squares at octaves with differing volumes to make new sounds
<br />
<br /><a href="http://nsf.4x86.com/nsfs/Sing_for_Absolution.nsf" class="postlink">dpcm triangle</a>
<br />
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/triangleechotest.nsf" class="postlink">Triange volume / echo using samples for delta counter nonsense</a>
<br />
